{"tid":1066361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵被轟大陸化 主席金句回帶：全世界都讚 係香港人鬧","createTime":"2019-03-18T00:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T02:00:54.000Z","uid":72009,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d4b9a39cde5cf62abadf602103cfbbc0ecb404","tid":1066361,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"港鐵今晨（18日）在收車後測試新信號系統期間，兩列車在中環站隧道內罕有攔腰相撞至出軌和冒煙，荃灣綫中環至金鐘站要全日停駛維修，同類事故是港鐵自1979年通車以來首次。網民紛留言批評港鐵「大陸化」，與曾爆出「動車追撞」事故的內地溫州「接軌」；亦有人回顧港鐵主席馬時亨1年前的「金句」：「全世界都讚我哋（港鐵），係香港人鬧我哋」、希望將所有乘客和港人「送去紐約同倫敦住一個禮拜，等佢哋搭當地嘅地鐵，返嚟就會覺得我哋香港（鐵路）好了」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22de311801f12b0a67f8106db6352b954cf5573e","tid":1066361,"uid":61547,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:45:17.000Z","msg":"事實港鐵真係唔差<br />\n去過外國旅行之後<br />\n班次密<br />\n價錢平"},{"pid":"9a0b88d863e5d89080f11f5df71d69970db5757b","tid":1066361,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:45:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12f164889398073b220ed728ad43c37b3c8cd0b6","tid":1066361,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c769dd7671dfd7f1ec85e4f39bb4da8515b79c2f","tid":1066361,"uid":214036,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0debe17d98b885c8255740ecdd0071ef93abf064","tid":1066361,"uid":61547,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c769dd7671dfd7f1ec85e4f39bb4da8515b79c2f","tid":1066361,"uid":214036,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"22de311801f12b0a67f8106db6352b954cf5573e","tid":1066361,"uid":61547,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:45:17.000Z","msg":"事實港鐵真係唔差<br />\n去過外國旅行之後<br />\n班次密<br />\n價錢平"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},